ActVeterans Review and Appeal Board Act
PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 2001-1456 of August 28, 2001 which will extend the term of appointment of VICTOR MARCHAND as a permanent member of the Veterans Review and Appeal Board until December 31, 2008; and designation of VICTOR MARCHAND of Charlottetown, Prince Edward Island, to be Chairperson of the Veterans Review and Appeal Board.
